{
  "stem": "17001.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The matter of fact, prior to that, there was an incident where we were digging the [HUNGARIAN] for the potatoes, and there were these big, husky Italian prisoners, and they were building the building.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And as I'm standing there in the-- in the gutter, or in the ditch, he's passing by.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he had his Italian uniform on him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he starts to shake himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I get so scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What is he shaking?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I look down, the beautiful boiled potatoes is dropping out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I hurriedly picked it up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he gave a big smile.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, my God.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is a miracle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, when we had a big air raid, as the bomb were coming, I know it is coming nearby, that they were living next to us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A little fence had divided the-- the two lager.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing was left of them except a wooden shoes, which I picked up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because by that time my shoes was going, and so and so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened is that when we were stealing the potatoes, and from the [HUNGARIAN], after that they caught the girl, or she was stupid enough to run into the soldier, we ran into this building what they were building, these Italians were building.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister-in-law emptied her potato.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She didn't have not one potatoes on her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hear the screaming and screaming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Quieted down.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we see that they coming out, and they are nailing in every shutter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever shutter was there, every shutter was nailed in except the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the bathroom, from the cold and the body heat, the steam formed an ice near the windows so they couldn't close the shutter.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They couldn't close the window either.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
